msg: Fix a problem reported by Hans Bakker, FreeMarker templates loaded using the Configuration object don't have access to the component:// notation reader and this causes them to fail because all templates now attempt to retrieve the html form macro library using that notation.  This is a quick fix but we should really fix the FreeMarkerViewHandler to load templates via the FreeMarkerWorker.
